mco.account.privacyinfo:
kulupu Mojan li pali mute tawa awen pi jan lili. pali ni li kepeken pali pi awen len pi jan lili (COPPA) li kepeken pali nasin pi awen pi nanpa ilo (GDPR).

ken la, sina wile kama lon ma Wen la, o toki tawa mama sina o sona e wile ona.

nimi musi sina li tan tenpo pini la (sina kama lon kepeken nimi sina), o tawa e nimi musi ni tawa nimi musi Mojan. ni la, sina ken kama lon ma Wen.
